           <div class="slide-cap left"> 
            <h2>Democrat MP Thepthai loses seat over election fraud</h2> 
            <div class="p">
              The Constitutional Court ordered Democrat MP Thepthai Senpong to give up his seat in Parliament on Wednesday, after he was sentenced to two years in prison for fraud during the Nakhon Si Thammarat mayoral election in 2014. 
            </div> 
           </div> </a> </li> 
         <li> <a target="_blank" href="https://www.nationthailand.com/news/30401886?utm_source=category&amp;utm_medium=internal_referral"> 
