           </div> 
           <div class="slide-cap left"> 
            <h2>52 hours allocated for censure debate: govt whip</h2> 
            <div class="p">
              The censure debate next month against 10 ministers will take 52 hours, the same as last year’s no-confidence motion, chief government whip and Palang Pracharath MP Wirach Ratanasate said on Wednesday. 
            </div> 
           </div> </a> </li> 
         <li> <a target="_blank" href="https://www.nationthailand.com/news/30401777?utm_source=category&amp;utm_medium=internal_referral"> 
