           </div> 
           <div class="slide-cap left"> 
            <h2>Siam Bioscience HQ hit with protest over vaccine deal </h2> 
            <div class="p">
              Ratsadon pro-democracy demonstrators led by Parit “Penguin” Chiwarak gathered outside Siam Bioscience’s Bangkok headquarters this afternoon to protest the company’s role in Thailand’s Covid-19 vaccine programme. 
            </div> 
           </div> </a> </li> 
         <li> <a target="_blank" href="https://www.nationthailand.com/news/30401765?utm_source=category&amp;utm_medium=internal_referral"> 
